ing: 2 cups cubed cooked chicken breast meat
1 (16 ounce) package frozen mixed vegetables, thawed
1 (10.75 ounce) can condensed cream of potato soup
1 (10.75 ounce) can condensed cream of chicken soup
des: "Easy, low in calories and good! Garnish with crumbled crackers."
ins: In a medium sauce pan combine chicken, mixed vegetables, cream of potato soup, cream of chicken soup and milk.  Heat through and serve with crumbled crackers on top.
